    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/8995bc8d1715bfccf2636241d695efd2.avif?t=1768668141\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mirror Layers </strong>是一款第一人称社交恐怖游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索神秘的12号公寓，与其他玩家合作解决具有挑战性的谜题，并在“镜子”中求生——那是一个被悲剧污染、扭曲的现实。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>社交恐怖体验</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/cb63ac1f14a5d4297003461afd5912fa.poster.avif?t=1768668141\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/cb63ac1f14a5d4297003461afd5912fa.webm?t=1768668141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Mirror Layers 中，你需要通过一个名为 Propaganda 的内置社交网络与其他玩家互动。你可以在其中分享建议、观点，尤其是物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏还提供手写笔记与拍照工具；记住，共享即生存！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/00a9915f65080d5e63b3766a92aebaf3.avif?t=1768668141\" width=86 height=86 /></span>Propaganda 的网页端/安卓端现已上线！即使不在 MirrorOS，也能与其他玩家协作！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>挑战性的谜题</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/93cf5ba126aecc593facd489b271e3ef.poster.avif?t=1768668141\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/93cf5ba126aecc593facd489b271e3ef.webm?t=1768668141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的重点是解决日益多样且复杂的谜题：探索环境、收集线索、关键物品，并通过 Propaganda 与他人合作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但要小心：一旦跨过镜子的门槛，你将不再安全</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>镜像现实</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/1474fd42ca1a9cb9d321b304f490025f.poster.avif?t=1768668141\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/1474fd42ca1a9cb9d321b304f490025f.webm?t=1768668141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >镜子背后的现实有许多方式会让你身陷危险。那里潜伏着一个生物，只凭本能寻找某样东西……也许是一部分的你？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，负面情绪弥漫于此处，黑暗过去的幽影将不断折磨你。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>故事</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/af850ee48b9afcb5eeb18e9d76b49372.poster.avif?t=1768668141\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/af850ee48b9afcb5eeb18e9d76b49372.webm?t=1768668141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Mirror Layers 中，玩家扮演的正是自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你收到了一份匿名邀请，要求你前往 Chandran 大楼的12号公寓——一栋奇异的16层建筑，其墙壁隐藏着一个黑暗的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会加入这场游戏吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>我们请求你给予我们你的一部分。你身份的一部分。</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/d1cd4f9b4203b47636fa0b3adb1ad215.poster.avif?t=1768668141\" width=600 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1490980/extras/d1cd4f9b4203b47636fa0b3adb1ad215.webm?t=1768668141\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我已经接触到了。你呢？你在等什么？</strong></p>",
